[Course_Description]
Direct mail marketing is more than just stuffing envelopes. In fact, direct mail (which is both inexpensive and easy to systematize) is the backbone of lead generation! In this course, learn how to build a scalable direct mail marketing system to boost your lead flow. Get step-by-step instruction on how to acquire leads through a targeted local mailing list, use direct mail to build an invisible selling machine, budget and craft a scalable direct marketing campaign, and much more. If you’re ready to build an invisible selling machine—and put your lead flow on autopilot—then this course can help you get started. This course was created by WealthFit. We are pleased to host this content in our library.